Package: giftR
Type: Package
Title: A Package to Assign & Notify Secret Santas
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Tim Szewczyk
Maintainer: Tim Szewczyk <tim.szewczyk@gmail.com>
Description: This package generates random assignments for a secret santa gift
    exchange. It incorporates couples so that significant others are not assigned
    to each other. Using the mailR package, it automatically sends emails to each
    participant to notify them of who they should give a gift to.
License: What license is it under?
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
